<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Includes information on:</p>

<ul>
  <li>how to get help medical help</li>
  <li>renewing prescriptions</li>
  <li>compulsory hospitalisation</li>
</ul>

<p>See also <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/foreign-travel-advice-for-people-with-mental-health-issues">foreign travel advice for people with mental health needs</a> and <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/mental-health">mental health and travelling abroad</a>.</p>
